&lt;p&gt;
KV2 fittings are used for commercial truck, transit, trailer and specialty vehicle markets. One-touch technology makes tube insertion (with strong tube holding force) and removal easier. KV2&apos;s patented seal allows tube cut angles to be well above the heavy vehicle industry standard. KV2 meets FMVSS 571.106, SAE J1131 and SAE J2494 standards.
&lt;/p&gt;

